Title: Camelia
Writer: Alexandre Dumas fils (novel), José Arenas, Edmundo Báez, Roberto Gavaldón, Gregorio Walerstein
Actors: María Félix, Jorge Mistral, Carlos Navarro, Renée Dumas
Plot: A woman of low estate is beloved of a promising young man, but sacrifices her love for him in order to protect his future and reputation.
